{
  "stem": "1929.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 576.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he went to a friend of his that used to-- he used to do business with.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And don't ask me his name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he had a little barrel-making factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "A barrel-making factory was, you know, making wooden barrels, like you put pickles in, and herring, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was a small place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Maybe he had 20, 30 people working for him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was two brothers, I think I remember, and a father that had that business.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my father used to sell them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Timber before the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he tol-- my brother told this man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, look, why don't you apply to the German authorities and get some permits so you can have Jews work for you?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He applied.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he got permission for 12 Jews to work there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my brother also tells me this story that before, he would get one of-- be one of the ones to come to work at that factory, they had to pay him off as well, so not only was he going to get free labor, but he was-- he also demanded some ransom money from us.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the major-- the major event in the ghetto was the fear of deportation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the communities just close to us were being deported.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I remember that almost everybody had some kind of a hiding place in their house, whether it was in the ceiling, or it was in the cellar, false walls, floors.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think we had something with a-- with a floor, just like in Everybody had a hiding place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And sometimes in around I think 1942, towards the end of '42, the Germans began what was called the Action.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
